experienceItems.title: Lead Software Engineer at Google
experienceItems.description: As a Senior Software Engineer at Google, I played a pivotal role in developing innovative solutions for Google's core search algorithms. Collaborating with a dynamic team of engineers, I contributed to the enhancement of search accuracy and efficiency, optimizing user experiences for millions of users worldwide.
